-formation" class="small-link no-underline white">Spiritual Formation</a><a href="/teamleader" class="small-link no-underline white">Team Leader</a><a href="#" class="small-link no-underline blog">VOUS&nbsp;Blog</a><a href="https://merch.vouschurch.com/" target="_blank" class="small-link no-underline white">Shop</a><a href="https://vouschurch.ccbchurch.com/goto/login" target="_blank" class="small-link no-underline white">Log In</a></div><div class="footer-column"><div class="small-p footer">MEDIA</div><a href="/online" class="small-link no-underline white">Church Online</a><a href="/watch" class="small-link no-underline white">Watch</a><a href="/blog" target="_blank" class="small-link no-underline white">Blog</a><a href="/worship" class="small-link no-underline white">VOUS Worship</a><a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/vous-church/id1042709241" target="_blank" class="small-link no-underline white">VOUS&nbsp;Podcast</a></div></div></div></div><div class="homepage-corner-banner conf hide"><img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/5f0cd5fb99f5470b194d3979/5fa48c9d32f6ac1d191d2bf7_close-button-dark.svg" loading="lazy" width="24" data-w-id="b4c569f0-f041-f67e-c37d-d32df1a6fd39" alt="" class="image-220"><div data-delay="4000" data-animation="slide" class="slider-4 w-slider" data-autoplay="true" data-easing="ease" data-hide-arrows="false" data-disable-swipe="false" data-autoplay-limit="0" data-nav-spacing="3" data-duration="500" data-infinite="true" role="region" aria-label="carousel"><div class="mask-8 w-slider-mask" id="w-slider-mask-1"><div class="slide-home w-slide" aria-label="1 of 2" role="group" style="transform: translateX(-422px); opacity: 1; transition: transform 500ms ease 0s;" aria-hidden="true"><div class="outline-cta-announcement-slide homepage" aria-hidden="true"><div class="homepage-banner-photo" aria-hidden="true"><img sizes="100vw" srcset="https://assets-global.website-files.com/5f0cd5fb99f5470b194d3979/632b718d2029e6792ac4f6fe_7Hero-p-